## ğŸ—‚ï¸ Data Model (SQL Schema)

```sql
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS weather_data (
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    temperature FLOAT,
    windspeed FLOAT,
    winddirection FLOAT,
    weathercode INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
